request.description:
The endpoint `{{API_URL}}master/locations/cities/lists` is a GET request that retrieves a list of cities with their corresponding IDs, states, countries, and full names.

### Response

The response will be a JSON array with the following schema:

``` json
[
  {
    "id": "string",
    "state": {
      "id": "string",
      "country": {
        "id": "string",
        "name": "string",
        "nameShort": "string"
      },
      "name": "string",
      "nameShort": "string"
    },
    "name": "string",
    "fullName": "string"
  }
]

 ```

This schema represents the structure of the response data, with each city containing an ID, state details, name, and full name.

### Create City

This endpoint is used to create a new city in the master locations.

#### Request

- Method: POST

- URL: {{API_URL}}master/locations/cities/create

- Body:

    - name (text, required): The name of the city.

    - stateId (text, required): The ID of the state to which the city belongs.

    - longitude (number, required): The longitude coordinate of the city.

    - latitude (number, required): The latitude coordinate of the city.


#### Response

The response is in JSON format and follows the schema below:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "tittle": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "message": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "id": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "state": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "id": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "country": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "id": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "name": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "nameShort": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "longitude": {
                  "type": "number"
                },
                "latitude": {
                  "type": "number"
                },
                "createdAt": {
                  "type": "string"
                }
              }
            },
            "name": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "nameShort": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "longitude": {
              "type": "number"
            },
            "latitude": {
