        },
        "longitude": {
          "type": "number"
        },
        "latitude": {
          "type": "number"
        },
        "createdAt": {
          "type": "string"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

### Update City Location

This endpoint allows the user to update the details of a specific city location.

#### Request Body

- `name` (string): The name of the city.

- `stateId` (string): The ID of the state to which the city belongs.

- `longitude` (number): The longitude coordinate of the city.

- `latitude` (number): The latitude coordinate of the city.


#### Response

The response will be a JSON object with the following schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "title": {"type": "string"},
    "message": {"type": "string"},
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "id": {"type": "string"},
        "state": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "id": {"type": "string"},
            "country": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "id": {"type": "string"},
                "name": {"type": "string"},
                "nameShort": {"type": "string"},
                "longitude": {"type": "number"},
                "latitude": {"type": "number"},
                "createdAt": {"type": "string"}
              }
            },
            "name": {"type": "string"},
            "nameShort": {"type": "string"},
            "longitude": {"type": "number"},
            "latitude": {"type": "number"},
            "createdAt": {"type": "string"}
          }
        },
        "name": {"type": "string"},
        "fullName": {"type": "string"},
        "longitude": {"type": "number"},
        "latitude": {"type": "number"},
        "createdAt": {"type": "string"}
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

### Create State

This endpoint allows the creation of a new state within a country.

#### Request Body

- name (string, required): The full name of the state.

- nameShort (string, required): The abbreviated name of the state.

- countryId (string, required): The unique identifier of the country to which the state belongs.

- longitude (number, required): The longitude coordinate of the state.

- latitude (number, required): The latitude coordinate of the state.


#### Response (JSON Schema)

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "title": { "type": "string" },
        "message": { "type": "string" },
        "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
                "id": { "type": "string" },
                "country": {
