    }
  }
}

 ```

### Update Department

This endpoint is used to update a specific department by sending an HTTP PUT request to the specified URL.

#### Request Body

- `name` (string): The full name of the department.

- `description` (string): The description of the department.

- `clientInfo` (boolean): Indicates whether client information is included.


The request body should be in the raw format with the following payload:

``` json
{
  "name": "updated value",
  "description": "updated value",
  "clientInfo": true
}

 ```

#### Response

The response of this request can be documented as a JSON schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "title": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "message": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "id": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "name": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "description": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "active": {
          "type": "boolean"
        },
        "createdAt": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "clientInfo": {
          "type": "boolean"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

